description:
Do you long for Heaven but fear the coming crisis? As the unprecedented events of 2020 unfolded, they served as a reminder of the times in which we live. Matthew Schanche thoughtfully explores the need to prepare ourselves mentally and spiritually, nurturing a heart filled with love to endure the times ahead. He delves into our obligation to share the truth with others and how to be securely grounded in Christ.
Matthew delves into the glories of Heaven, a spectacular place of personal growth and eternal progress. He uplifts the heart with God's promises of guidance, strength, and protection for challenging times in the future. Join Matt and discover that as the great controversy is drawing to a close, it is crucial to now know God's word and anchor our salvation!
